# my.onSocketOpen

2022-07-03 18:44

Use this API to listen to the event of enabling the WebSocket connection.

## Sample Code

copy

```javascript
my.connectSocket({
  url: 'test.php',
});

my.onSocketOpen(function(res) {
  console.log('The WebSocket connection is enabled!');
});
```

**Note:** The case is only for reference. Please use your own URL to test.

## Parameters

|     |     |     |     |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Property** | **Type** | **Required** | **Description** |
| callback | Function | Yes | The callback function for the event of enabling the WebSocket connection. |
